&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We’re in this for the greater good at ParetoHealth. Our mission is collective greatness, nothing less will do. Our team is a single force united in the drive to transform employee health benefits.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
