&lt;p&gt;At ParetoHealth, underwriting isn’t back-office — it’s front and center. Our team is the backbone of our mission to reinvent stop-loss insurance and empower midsize employers to take control of their healthcare costs. And we’re growing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whether you&#39;re new to underwriting or bring years of experience — especially in medical underwriting, stop-loss, or self-funded plans — we want to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;🔍 What We Look For:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in medical underwriting (stop-loss/self-funded plan experience is a plus)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sharp analytical skills and comfort with data-driven decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curiosity, ownership mindset, and a desire to be part of something bigger&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
