&lt;p&gt;This individual will serve as the internal integrator for a new Pareto product — translating strategy into cross-functional execution across underwriting, partner management, onboarding, client management, renewals, and governance. &amp;nbsp;This is &lt;em&gt;not &lt;/em&gt;a back-office operations role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;What You’ll Own:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Build the Product Operating System&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Design and implement scalable workflows across underwriting, onboarding, renewals, customer and partner operations.&lt;br&gt;- Establish governance cadence (SteerCo, OKRs, dashboards, decision logs).&lt;br&gt;- Improve operational visibility and reduce friction as the business scales.&lt;br&gt;- Ensure infrastructure supports 2–3x growth without operational instability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lead Operational Partner Management&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Serve as day-to-day operational counterpart to TPAs and stop-loss carriers.&lt;br&gt;- Run structured performance reviews and escalation processes.&lt;br&gt;- Maintain accountability to service expectations and contractual mechanics.&lt;br&gt;- Ensure operational readiness for new partner launches.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Translate Expansion into Execution&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Own rollout plans for new TPAs, stop-loss carriers, markets, and program enhancements.&lt;br&gt;- Align underwriting, commercial, product, operations, and finance stakeholders.&lt;br&gt;- Identify risks early and drive resolution.&lt;br&gt;- Deliver clean, on-time implementation of approved initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;What Success Looks Like (12–18 Months)&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The new product solutions operate through defined systems, not tribal knowledge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross-functional teams execute with clarity and accountability.&lt;/li&gt

